title: 02On the way back home
lyrics:
Instrumental Intro

Verse 1
On the way back home after seeing you off
I walk slowly feeling the regret
Your scent still lingers on me
and I keep thinking of you more and more
The day feels way too short

On the bus ride home
leaning against the window lost in thoughts of you
Just as I reach for my phone in my pocket
your Goodbye message makes me smile again

The night breeze blowing through the window
touches my heart and your voice
still lingers in my ears
I keep thinking of you more and more

I wish time could  just stop here
I want to run to you right now

Bridge

Verse 2
On the way back home after seeing you off
I suddenly stop while walking down the street
Missing you I turn around again
My heart is still with you
waiting for the day we meet again

Back home lying in bed
I think of every moment we shared
My mind is filled with thoughts of you
a smile spreads across my face
A night where excitement keeps me from sleeping

The night breeze blowing through the window
touches my heart and your voice
still lingers in my ears
I keep thinking of you more and more

I wish time could  just stop here
I want to run to you right now

lyrics:
Music and Lyrics    
  The Left Hand Tree

A flickering jewel amber light
Suspended in twilight thoughts
A whisper caught between here and gone
You sense it an amethyst dream
Softly glowing calling you near
But as you reach it slips away
A fragile whisper retreating unclear

it closes
heartbeat delicate

Forever present forever absent
A silent echo that lingers in the mind

You pause let go release the need
And in that surrender it blooms
Tentative and soft as if to test
The waters of your calm your quiet rest
But the blue turns cloudy the vision shifts
Obscured by the fog of unfulfilled dreams
It slips through the cracks of thought
Becoming one with the vast unseen

This delicate dance of desire and release
A push a pull a silent tease
It remains an everdistant glow
A beauty both real and imagined
Hovering just beyond reach
A reminder of the art of letting go

It opens
it closes
heartbeat delicate

A touch and it recoils a breath away

A silent echo that lingers in the mind

A fleeting glimpse of what could be
A jewel in the twilight a thought on the edge
Forever shimmering forever unseen
In the quiet of your mind it stays
A reminder of the beauty in letting go
Hovering in the space between
Where dreams dissolve and echoes flow

it closes

title: Banshees Wail
lyrics:
Instrumental Prelude





Banshee  female soprano
Fogshrouded hills echo my keen
Harbinger of fates unseen
My voice  a dirge a gale a hush
For those who heed their fates I crush

Mortal  male tenor
What ghostly notes slice through the gloom
My spine iceclad my breath entombed
Pale herald why this midnight verse
What grim tidings do you rehearse

Duet  Interweaving
Dusks frontier blurs two realms apart
No refuge from the reapers art
A requiem of dread foretold
Where human fear and kismet fold

Banshee  female soprano
Fleshbound soul shun my refrain
Those who listen court their bane
My lament scripts tomorrows page
A drama none can upstage

Mortal  male tenor
Wraith of twilight Im ensnared
Is this eve my thread is sheared
Your dirge ignites a primal dread
What horrors loom in hours ahead

Duet  Building intensity
In this hour as phantoms loom
We pirouette on brinks of doom
Your cry my terror both entwined
As life and death their paths aligned

Banshee  female soprano
No spite I bear no bliss I know
My role the final curtains show
A warning knell of pending ends
Before the veil of time transcends

Mortal  male tenor
Oh specter pale with tresses wild
Your song leaves mortal hearts defiled
If night must claim me let it be
But grant one final rhapsody

Duet  Climax
Voices merge in an otherworldly harmony
In twilights realm where banshees keen
And mortal courage wanes unseen
Our voices twine  both fate and fright
As deaths cold whisper claims the night

title: bara di antara kita
lyrics:
Langit kelam di atas kita  
Jalan terjal di depan mata  
Kau dan aku berdiri berdua  
Dalam cinta yang tak mudah penuh luka

We fight we fall we bleed we rise  
In every scar I see your eyes  
Kita bertahan meski terluka  
Karena cinta ini lebih dari katakata


Bara di antara kita takkan pernah padam  
Dalam gelap kita temukan jalan  
Meski badai menghadang kita terus berjuang  
Cinta ini butuh keberanian takkan tergoyahkan

Through fire and storm well stand our ground  
In every heartbeat our love resounds  
Dengan tekad kita maju melawan  
Walau dunia tak berpihak kita tetap bertahan


Beribu kata beribu janji  
Tak cukup melukiskan semua ini  
Ada rasa sakit ada perih  
Tapi dalam genggamanmu aku takkan letih

The shadows try to tear us down  
But in the dark youre my only sound  
Setiap langkah membawa kita lebih dekat  
Menghadapi dunia cinta kita semakin kuat


Tak ada cinta tanpa pengorbanan  
Setiap luka menjadi bukti perjalanan  
Dan dalam setiap tarikan nafas  
Kita temukan harapan di tengah gelap

With every fall we rise again  
In your eyes I find the end and begin  
Aku dan kamu melawan waktu  
Meski dunia hancur kita tetap satu


Bara di antara kita menyala tanpa henti  
Dalam perjuangan ini kita temukan arti  
Dengan keberanian kita hadapi takdir  
Cinta ini kuat takkan pernah berakhir

Flames between us burning bright  
Through every storm we find our light  
Dalam setiap tantangan kita berpegangan  
Dengan kesabaran dan cinta kita terus bertahan


Di ujung jalan meski gelap menghadang  
Aku dan kamu bertahan dan terbang  
With you Ill fight till the end of time  
In this battle of love youre forever mine  
Bara cinta ini takkan pernah padam  
Dalam setiap detak kita tetap seirama

title: Beef Diplomat  Gone
lyrics: Sometimes you just want to be gone

title: Beneath the Surface
lyrics:
Verse 1
In mornings glow your face appears
But shadows twist and feed my fears
You carved a wound that time cant heal
Drowning in the words we failed to feel
You swore youd stay youd never leave
But now I stand with shattered beliefs
The silence screams louder than lies
Exposing truths behind your eyes

PreChorus
And Im digging through the wreckage
Trying to find the parts of me
Buried deep beneath the surface
Where you left your broken dreams

Chorus
Cause underneath the surface
Theres a fire still burning
Every tear I never cried
Every word I kept inside
Yeah beneath the surface
Theres a pain that Im learning
All the pieces that remain
Are the ones you couldnt take
But you cant see whats underneath
No you cant see WHATS UNDERNEATH

Verse 2
Heard your name on the radio
A ghostly echo of the love we used to know
I rewind the days when we were whole
But every memory now just pierces my soul
You promised truth would be our guide
But all it did was wound and divide
Now every breath feels like a war
To keep from sinking into the dark once more

PreChorus
And Im lost in all these questions

title: Brave face
lyrics:

Twentyseven candles on my last birthday cake

I nod and smile what else can I say
Repeat Chorus

Bridge

I let the tears fall no use fighting my will
Cause being strong dont mean you cant break
And healing starts when you give your heart a break
Verse 5
Im not made of stone Im flesh and bone
Realizing now I dont have to face this alone
Grandpa taught me strength now hes teaching me grace
As I learn to live beyond this brave face
Verse 6

Wondering how much time we have left to share
But then I see his smile hear his gentle voice
Reminding me that love is always a choice
Repeat Chorus

Outro

Im just learning how to cry
But maybe thats alright
Cause at least Im learning to try
And through it all I know one things true
Grandpa this brave face its all for you

title: Claire Comes Ashore
lyrics:
Low pressure moving in and winds are picking up
Should we call it Is it too much 

Feet step nimbly over lines on docks dappled with the first drops
Worried looks among the crew
But weve come too far Well see it through

A cold splash from the rough and briny sea makes us feel alive
Now its lines and helm plan the tack
Focus girls were underway

The other team from the east coast
Theyre used to this and it shows 
We struggle to keep up

Chopping waves toss and bounce then all at once
We drop
Time stands still and we stare into the mouth of a giant
I wonder what I will hit when it hits us 

A moment a face an image which will last forever
The last moment I wish I could hold on
But the moment is gone 

Why am I here with a light blinking on my shoulder
Floating far from the people I love

They pull me up Dads strong arms the only steady thing in the stormy sea
Eyes wide straining through the stinging wind and salty spray
She was there with me
I still see her face
Where is she now

Her fathers voice screams her name with a panic I have never heard
Everything in him struggling to push through a hole too small to get out and find her
Where is she
Where is she

It never felt like long enough How could we let go

title: Death Glade
lyrics:
Through haunted woods in midnights breath
Where branches twist and mourn the dead
The whispers rise from ancient graves
A spectral dance in deaths dark glade

Under hollow trees where night birds sing
The ground splits wide a blackened sea
A murmur runs through moss and stone
A whispered curse forever sown

In the silence of the fallen leaves
Where the moonlight weaves its silver threads
We wander lost in endless dreams
Bound to the darkness forever wed

A spectral mist the forests veil
It hides the path it tells no tale
The winds lament a ghostly cry
For those who lived for those who died

Beneath the boughs of ageless trees
A hollowed ground that no one sees
The secrets kept the blood thats spilled
The broken hearts the earth have filled

In the silence of the fallen leaves
Where the moonlight weaves its silver threads
We wander lost in endless dreams
Bound to the darkness forever wed

The glade a ghost within my mind
A prison where no rest I find
Lost in this bleak and endless gloom
I gasp for air escape the tomb
These winding paths my thoughts retrace
A forest born of fears embrace
In darkness trapped I walk alone
Fragments of a past once known
The weight of silence drags me down
A captive soul I start to drown
No dawn to chase this lifeless gray
Just the void where my nightmares lay

In the silence of the fallen leaves
Where the moonlight weaves its silver threads
We wander lost in endless dreams
Bound to the darkness forever wed

title: Deep in the Forest
lyrics:
All of our study and work and struggle

Just to grow a tiny microbe in the unforgiving soil 
One tiny block to build a world

Now this  how can I take it all in
This forest that stretches beyond horizons 
Built upon epochs from microbes to mammals 
So deeply complex profoundly beautiful 

And here I am part of it Nay not part 
The bounds of self and system blur
One living mass richly composed
A feeling too primal for words

We live

title: Discord Dreams
lyrics:
Verse 1
Sa mundo ng pixels at virtual na pangarap  
Si Angelika ang nagniningning siyay kasama sa winning team  
Tahimik ang kilos pero malakas ang gawa  
Sa mga laban ng Valorant siyay nagiisa sa gitna ng madla

 PreChorus
Naglalive sa Discord may husay at biyaya  
Isang Filipina star siyay nangunguna  
Sa 3D art magic kanyang mga likhay kamanghamangha  
Sa kulturang Pinoy siyay nananatilit nagmamalaki

 Chorus
Si Angelika Aduna may pusong gamer Manny Pacquiao  
Sa bawat laban siyay lumalaban ng buo Role player  
Tahimik sa kalikasan pero matapang sa screen Ferocious  
Ang ating Pinoy queen sa digital na eksena Mabuhaaaaaaay

 Verse 2
Mula sa mga isla ng Pilipinas siyay humuhugot ng lakas  
May passion sa gaming na walang hanggan  
Gumagawa ng mga mundo sa 3D napakakulay at liwanag  
Siyay tunay na artista sa araw at gabi

 PreChorus
Naglalive sa Discord kung saan nagkakaisa ang mga kaibigan  
Sa bawat laro siyay nagpapakita ng galing  
Sa mga laban ng Valorant siyay nangunguna ng may pagmamalaki  
Ang talento ni Angelika hindi matatago

 Chorus
Si Angelika Aduna may pusong gamer Manny Pacquiao  
Sa bawat laban siyay lumalaban ng buo Role player  
Tahimik sa kalikasan pero matapang sa screen Ferocious  
Ang ating Pinoy queen sa digital na eksena Mabuhaaaaaaay

 Bridge
Sa mundo ng gaming siyay isang nagniningning na bituin  
Sa bawat tagumpay itinaas niya ang antas  
Isang tahimik na puwersa na may malakas na boses  
Si Angelika Aduna narito kung saan siya nararapat

 Chorus
Si Angelika Aduna may pusong gamer Manny Pacquiao  
Sa bawat laban siyay lumalaban ng buo Role player  
Tahimik sa kalikasan pero matapang sa screen Ferocious  
Ang ating Pinoy queen sa digital na eksena Mabuhaaaaaaay

 Outro
Sa puso ng laro siyay nakakahanap ng lugar  
Si Angelika Aduna puno ng biyaya  
Mula sa Pilipinas sa buong mundo  
Isang gamer isang artista ating ipinagmamalaki

title: Discovering the Lava Tubes
lyrics:
Dusty red skies 
Blaze and freeze 
At the same time

A canyon opens up before us 
So impossibly huge our minds cannot quite take it in
Swallowed in a wilderness so brave and gorgeous 

I think were here 
Comes a crackle on the radio 

Yeah this is it for sure 
Entrance to the lava tube

Cant wait to get inside and see what secrets it may hide
Could be the home that weve been looking for 

The wind picks up and James gives me that look he always has 
When hes worried but trying to look calm
Telltale signs of a storm 
The kind that catches you out cold
Hunker down and pray to Mars is all you can do

They say these tubes will be a haven from the storms
Well nows our chance
Lets go and test them 

We step inside and flick on lights
Chased by clouds of dust as we descend 
But soon a quietness surrounds us
The tubes mighty walls defiant of the storm

A simple space
Long and straight 
Stretches out before us
Here and there interrupted by a mass of fallen rock

In my mind I see homes and habitats 
For plants and spaces for the labs

A safe retreat an anchor point a home

Shadows fall they know my name
Wings spread wide theres none to blame

But who are they to judge me

title: I Knew You When
lyrics:
We were young chasing dreams down empty streets
You and I always dancing to our own heartbeat
Wild nights under stars that never seemed to fade
We swore wed never change wed never be afraid

I remember when you were my everything

Now I see the shadows where you used to stand
And Im just a whisper slipping through your hands

I knew you before the world weighed you down

I knew you when your dreams were still intact
Before the colors faded to black

I remember when you were my everything
When we were invincible we could take on anything
Now I see the shadows where you used to stand
And Im just a whisper slipping through your hands

We were young and the world was at our feet
Now I walk these empty streets alone incomplete

lyrics:
A fleeting thought that seems to fit
A mad dash for a scrap of anything to catch before its gone 

That thought  that flash that glimpse of clarity 
Could it work Could it really be 
What if

Yes this looks real
This could work

Racing to the lab down dark streets past closed shops

Making breakfast while I make history

I must catch it while theres time

Before a detail slips away 
Jot and tittle every piece to make the arc complete 
This story is everything we need

There it is laid out before me Mapped and captured safely stowed
On chalkboard scrap and manicsounding voice memos

But will it work

title: Lifes Wild Ride
lyrics:

No chains to tether free spirit wild
Im not a ghost a story compiled

title: Mars Resistance
lyrics:
You dont know what its like to sustain 
Till youve lived on a vast barren plain 
To use only what you can replace 
To create everything from dust and waste

Youve trashed your own world 
Why trust you with ours
Keep your politics your mandates and lies

We lived on science since we were knee high 
Its our life blood our only way to survive 
So dont come here and tell us you know
Cause we know you dont care for the truth

Resource independence threatens autocracy 
So you pick papers to back up your policies 
That slow down progress and keep us safe 
In your infinite wisdom from 140 million miles away

title: Only a Dream
lyrics:
Verse 1
I finally found someone who wanted to stay  
To love me through the darkest day  
Someone to hold to pull me near  
To chase away all the lingering fear

PreChorus

I thought this was it I thought it was true  
But then I woke and I lost you

Chorus
It was only a dream nothing more  
And now Im more broken than before  
I found someone to hold to keep out the cold  
But now Im alone and its taking its toll  
You were just a vision fading away  
And Im left with nothing but the pain of the day

Verse 2
I heard your voice soft in the night  
Whispering promises making it right  
But when I reached out you slipped from my grasp  
A fleeting memory I couldnt clasp

PreChorus
Now the silence is louder than before  
The emptiness cuts right to the core  
I thought I had found what I longed for  
But you were a dream nothing more

Chorus

And now Im more broken than before  
I found someone to hold to keep out the cold  
But now Im alone and its taking its toll  
You were just a vision fading away  
And Im left with nothing but the pain of the day

Bridge
How cruel is the mind to give whats not there  
To show me love then leave me in despair  
Now Im left with this aching inside  
A love that was never mine to find

Chorus Reprise
It was only a dream nothing more  
And now Im more broken than before  
I found someone to hold to keep out the cold  
But now Im alone and its taking its toll  
You were just a vision fading away  
And Im left with nothing but the pain of the day

Outro
I woke to the truth and its harder to bear  
For love was a dream and now Im left with despair

title: Placebo
lyrics:
Chibiitaii


Placebo a feeble hope
Not a rope not a needle
Something idle like believing
In a false idol while youre grieving
While youre bleeding alone in an aisle
Gone on an isle blood starts flowing
Between tiles now its pouring

Running miles and not eating
The signs start showing now youre hiding
Under layers to avoid the stares
Nobody cares theyre just faking
Their compassion

Not an object nor a person
Taking every comment as an aggression
Feeling trapped in an endless session
A dark lesson learned in isolation
Every question an accusation
Every glance an interrogation

No salvation just damnation
In a world full of hesitation
Where connection feels like deception
And love is just a faded reflection
Of something that once had meaning
Now its fleeting just deceiving
Like the placebo a hollow feeling

Running miles and not eating
The signs start showing now youre hiding
Under layers to avoid the stares
Nobody cares theyre just faking
Their compassion

Every step feels like a stumble
Every breath makes you crumble
Every promise turns to rubble
In a mind thats always troubled
Seeking solace in the silence
But finding only violence
In the echoes of your thoughts
Tangled up twisted and caught

In a web of doubt and fear
Wondering why youre still here
Why the voices wont disappear
Why the pain is always near
Grasping at straws reaching for air
In a world that doesnt care
Hoping for a savior but finding despair
In every corner everywhere

But you keep going keep surviving
Through the darkness keep striving
Even when the hope feels idle
Like believing in a false idol
You keep walking keep breathing
Through the pain through the grieving
Because even in the darkest night
Theres a flicker of distant light

title: Ringmaster Halloween song
lyrics:
Step into the quiet storm where strings are pulled and minds are torn
The lights flicker a fleeting grace
But you cant hide inside this place

Under my hand your world obeys
Your thoughts twist in a thousand ways
You think you see the open gate
But love the weavers sealed your fate
I pull the threads your will unwinds
Your freedoms just a mask youll find
Each word I speak it sinks like stone
Do you still think youre all alone

The noose tightens you gasp for air
I welcome you inside my lair

Im the one who whispers in your ear
Im the puppetmaster feeding on your fear
Try to run but the road loops back
Youre walking on a thread about to snap
Your heart beats in time with my command
Dance for me now youre in my hands
The wheel spins on but the game is rigged
Youre the prize Ill never break or save

You say youll leave  oh what a dream
But love your minds not what it seems
Each word you utter I reshape with glee
Your every cry is trapped before its free
The shadows of your past pursue
Are threads I use to bind you true
Do you trust what your eyes betray
The shows not done  youre here to stay

The noose tightens you gasp for air
I welcome you inside my lair

Im the one who whispers in your ear
Im the puppetmaster feeding on your fear
Try to run but the road loops back
Youre walking on a thread about to snap
Your heart beats in time with my command
Dance for me now youre in my hands
The wheel spins on but the game is rigged
Youre the prize Ill never break or save

I pull the strings that shape your fall
You think youve stood but you still crawl
The trap is sprung you cant break free
Your path is set you belong to me

How sweet it is your hope unwinds
You see my shadow in your mind
Each lie you tell yourself to flee
Is just another gift from me
You say youll leave  I once dreamed that too
But love this prisons all we ever knew
Do you see yourself in my haunted eyes
The show goes on  were both trapped inside

Spin
The chains are tight
Twist
You lose the fight
Kneel
The game is played
Scream
But youre betrayed
Cry
Its far too late
Run
But youre doomed to stay

Im the one who whispers in your ear
Im the puppetmaster feeding on your fear
Old scars twist the cycle tight
Youre bound to the dark lost in the night
Your heart beats in time with my cruel design
Dance for me now youre forever mine
The wheel spins on and youll never escape
Youre the prize of my wrath your fates been shaped

title: Shattered Sovereignty
lyrics:
Shadows rising fast
Blackened skies they cast
Summon the abyss
Shattered faith your last


Twisting metal screaming pain
Echoes through a darkened plain
Crimson rain it spills like wine
Death is where the heart aligns



In the heart of the storm where the shadows converge
The Elden Ring splintered a dark fateful purge
Demigods rise fueled by ambition and wrath
A serpents embrace weaves a treacherous path


Echoes of war the heavens ablaze
Rivers of blood mark the end of the days
From ashes we rise a new order to claim
In the chaos of power well carve out our names


Malenia strikes with a venomous bite
Blades like the wind dancing through the night
Her whispers entwined in the hearts of the lost
A symphony of shadows at what cost


Echoes of war the heavens ablaze
Rivers of blood mark the end of the days
From ashes we rise a new order to claim
In the chaos of power well carve out our names

Wielding the fragments of a divine shattered light
Through fields of despair through the cries of the slain
We march on the ruins through suffering and pain


Radahn fell from grace a star now obscured
His legacy twisted his fate so assured
Rykard feasts on the essence of dreams
Devouring the fallen unraveling seams


Echoes of war the heavens ablaze
Rivers of blood mark the end of the days

title: Sins of the Father
lyrics:
Instrumental Intro
A slow fingerpicked acoustic guitar builds the mood Banjo enters adding a rhythmic layer and the kick drum slowly fades in setting the stage for the verse
























Verse 1
I walk this road these hands unclean
The weight of blood Ive never seen
A shadow falls where light should be
The sins of the father are chasing me

PreChorus
Oh they said the past wont bind
But I feel it in my bones tonight

Chorus
The sins of the father they pull like chains
Through fire and flood and pouring rain
No matter how far no matter how fast
The sins of the father they always last

Instrumental Break
A rhythmic instrumental section follows with the banjo and guitar driving forward picking up the pace The sound intensifies creating momentum before the next verse

Verse 2
His voice is gone but the echoes stay
I hear his whispers in every prayer I say
I carry the guilt I didnt choose
The sins of the father I cannot lose

PreChorus
Oh they said the past wont bind
But I feel it in my bones tonight

Chorus
The sins of the father they pull like chains
Through fire and flood and pouring rain
No matter how far no matter how fast
The sins of the father they always last

Instrumental Break leading to Bridge
A dramatic break with the banjo picking up speed accompanied by a pounding kick drum and fast strumming Builds tension as it leads into the emotional bridge

Bridge
And oh I cry but it wont set me free
The sins of the father are bound to me
And oh I scream but it wont change a thing
The sins of the father are everything

Solo after Bridge
Banjo and guitar take center stage here in a powerful instrumental solo The tempo increases with stomping rhythm and fast picking showcasing raw energy and emotion

Final Chorus
The sins of the father they pull like chains
Through fire and flood and pouring rain
No matter how far no matter how fast
The sins of the father they always last

Instrumental Outro
A slow mournful outro with the banjo softly picking as the kick drum fades The guitar strums gently echoing the weight of the final lines fading out into silence

Fade to nothing but wind

title: Strawberries and Spaceships
lyrics:
Female voice
Charlotte Claire come and see 
Theres a brand new strawberry

Plant in our pot branching out from the old 
A runner reaching searching for a hold
Somewhere to put down roots and make a home
A new place to grow another chance for survival

Young female voice
Oh look mom The new one has a flower 
Lets give them all a gentle shower
Water sun and weeks go by
Pretty soon the pot is full 

Runners reach touch down and grow
Flowers berries bellies full 

Male voice
Charlotte Claire come and see
Theres a rocket launching on TV

Explorers climbed aboard today
And headed into outer space
Theyre going to the moon to see
If we can make a colony

A foothold to survive in space
A stepping stone this lunar base
Will be our gateway to the stars
Today the moon tomorrow Mars

Runners reach touch down and grow
Life roots and home in a new soil

title: The Last Ride
lyrics:
Instrumental Intro
A slow ominous start with deep resonant cello notes and soft banjo plucking The mood is heavy like the weight of inevitability















Verse 1

Black curtains drawn and I can feel the heat

Instrumental Break
A haunting instrumental break with a slow banjo lead and the cello underscoring the tension leading into the next verse

Verse 2

But I plead with death say Im not to blame

Dont send me to the ground dont bury me today

All the wrong Ive done it wasnt what I meant

Dont drag me to the dark dont end this light

Chorus

The begging the crying the pleas for more
You cheated you stole left blood in your wake
Now the hearse is here and the rides yours to take

Instrumental Break before Bridge
The banjo picks up pace giving a sense of a fastapproaching end the cello creating a tense heavy atmosphere

Bridge Continued
The roads grown short and the light fades away
Death grips my soul and theres nothing left to say
I scream to the night but my voice is gone
Now I see the truth Ive been damned all along

Solo after Bridge
A sorrowful haunting banjo solo building tension as it leads into the final chorus the feeling of inescapable fate closing in

Chorus
He says I know what youve done every lie every sin
The cheating the stealing the blood on your skin
This is your last ride theres no turning back
In the end every sinner walks this track

Instrumental Outro
The song ends with a slow eerie instrumental fadeout banjo picking over a mournful cello as the hearse drives into the distance carrying the weight of regret and finality

title: The Music Box
lyrics:
In this cold room on a dreary day 
Raindrops fall like tears they lay 
Gazing at the floor a plank catches my eye 
Curious I lift it and dust starts to fly

Beneath it a music box under the beam 
Gently I open it as if in a dream 
A soft melody plays a lullaby song 
Bringing back memories where they belong

Oh dance little ballerina 
Carry me from my daily arena 
In this enchanted world all is clear 
The blues evaporate I shed no tear

Memories of laughter of summers to dream
 Fairy tales told by the stream 
My mothers voice singing 
so sweet and strong 
Each note a lesson where I belong

Oh dance little ballerina 
Carry me from my daily arena 
In this enchanted world all is clear 
The blues evaporate I shed no tear

As clouds part the rain dissipates 
In the box the past it narrates 
Laughter and dreams without any fear
Each melody transports me far from here

Now each step I take light as a feather 
Dancing on sunbeams regardless of weather 
In this glow shadows all have fled The warmth of joy 
like sunlight spread A radiant heat fills up the space 
As smiles light up my quiet place 
The music wraps me in a warm embrace Transporting me to the sunlight

come with me

In this frozen moment hope does appear 
My room now warm as if someone near 
I am the ballerina spinning around 
In lifes ballet where joy is found

Oh dance little ballerina 
Carry me from my daily arena
 In this enchanted world all is clear 
The blues evaporate I shed no tear

Oh dance little ballerina 
Carry me from my daily arena
 In this enchanted world all is clear 
The blues evaporate I shed no tear

When the music ends and silence falls 
I cherish the memories within these walls
 In the cold room now filled with light 
The musics healed me brought me to height

title: Threshold to Madness II
lyrics:
Disturbing unsettling Intro

Concept
This song is envisioned as an auditory journey through ancient and forgotten rituals 

Spoken Whispered
Day One
Subject David neuroscientist
Obsessed with consciousness the minds abyss
Unearthing secrets a classified file
Project Abyss

Spoken Whispered
Day Two
Subject Adam physicist sharp mind
Joins the experiment eager to unwind
The mysteries of perception the psyches maze
Unaware of the impending soulcrushing phase

Instrumental

Spoken Whispered
Day Ten
All subjects express a growing unease
Shadows in the corner a presence to displease
Inexplicable visions a figure with no form
The boundaries of reality begin to deform

Spoken Whispered
Day Fifteen
Subliminal horrors primeval fears arise
The subjects scream in anguish their sanity capsized
Babbling incoherently of a truth beyond comprehension
An ancient indifferent force a cosmic abomination

breakdown

Spoken Whispered
Day Twenty
Subjects vanish one by one consumed by dread
Those who remain their minds have fled
Researchers try to pull the plug but its too late
The threshold of madness an inescapable fate

Solo
David the sole survivor a husk of a man
Burdened by the knowledge a curse to withstand
He tries to warn others to share his plight
But those who listen are dragged into the night

Chorus
If you see a shadow cast by nothing at all
Avert your gaze dont heed its call
For once it sees you your mind will crack
The threshold of madness will leave its track

Solo
Researchers Note
The experiment is sealed the files destroyed
But the horror lingers a malevolent void
A warning to the curious a cautionary tale
The price of forbidden knowledge a sanitys bale

Outro
In the echoes of madness a whisper persists
Of an eldritch truth that forever twists
The fabric of reality the human minds demise
Beware the shadows cast by unseeable guise

Tear it apart
